data.description: Charming townhouse near KSU and golf course.  Great roommate plan since both bedrooms have private bathrooms and large closets. Lower level has laminate flooring. Entry into great room with cozy brick fireplace. Kitchen is open to the dining area and has a pantry and lots of storage. Laundry closet on the main level.  Large fenced back yard with privacy fence.  Parking pad has room for 2 cars. No HOA or rental restrictions. Short walk to KSU Big Owl bus line. Photos being taken next week.
